These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, 7up, fanta
House: wooden, colonial, art-deco, ranch-style
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, rabbit, rat
There 4 different types of food: pepper, pear, peach, grapes
City: nizza, marseilles, new-york, miami
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 3. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
 5. the ranch-style house is the ranch-style house##1
 6. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 8. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person eating pear##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
10. the wooden house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
12. the owner of the rabbit is between the art-deco house and the owner of the dog##2
13. the person drinking 7up is the person traveling to miami##1
14. the person traveling to new-york is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
15. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage           | soy-milk | 7up | fanta  | hot-chocolate    |
| House   | colonial     | ranch-style   | art-deco  | wooden  |
| Pet           | dog        | rabbit    | rat        | chinchilla |
| Food         | grapes    | pear      | pepper   | peach    |
| City     | nizza  | miami     | marseilles | new-york |

