.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, juice, sprite
4 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, whist, chess
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, blend, alhambra, havana
House: victorian, colonial, craftsman, futuristic
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, writer, manager, firefighter
 1. the scientist is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 3. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
 4. the futuristic house is on the left of the manager##1
 5. the havana-smoker is the writer##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
 8. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 9. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
10. the person playing canasta is the firefighter##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
12. the victorian house is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
13. the colonial house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice        | sprite       | cola    | fanta       |
| Game         | whist | backgammon      | chess | canasta |
| Cigar   | havana     | alhambra | blend  | dunhill   |
| House   | colonial   | futuristic         | victorian   | craftsman      |
| Job         | writer      | scientist     | manager    | firefighter      |

