.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-3::.
City: venice, new-york, colone, miami
House: townhouse, ranch-style, colonial, futuristic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, house, indie, jazz
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, water, lemonade, almond-milk
4 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, goldfish, fish
 1. the person drinking water is the fan of house##1
 2. the fan of house is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 6. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 7. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 8. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 9. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
10. the person traveling to colone is the fan of indie##1
11. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person drinking water##1
12. the fan of jazz is on the right of the colonial house##1
13. the person drinking lemonade is the person traveling to miami##1
14. the fan of indie is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| City          | colone | new-york | venice     | miami |
| House           | colonial  | futuristic   | townhouse | ranch-style  |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | jazz      | house     | country   |
| Beverage         | almond-milk | coffee  | water   | lemonade    |
| Pet     | goldfish | turtle    | fish     | frog |

