.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-4::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, radish, corn, kiwi
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, apricot, light-blue, yellow
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, reggae, rock, trance
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, coffee, soy-milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, montecristo, aristoff, cain
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 2. the fan of rock is the person eating corn##1
 3. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 4. the fan of trance is between the baccarat-smoker and the aristoff-smoker##2
 5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
 6. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the montecristo-smoker##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
10. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
11. the person who likes yellow is in an odd position##4
12. the person eating banana is the person who likes yellow##1
13. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
14. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
15. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |        4        |
| Food         | kiwi | radish    | banana | corn       |
| Color           | apricot | pink  | yellow   | light-blue |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | reggae     | trance      | rock            |
| Beverage           | cola       | coffee      | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk           |
| Cigar     | cain      | aristoff | montecristo   | baccarat         |

