.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-5::.
House: farmhouse, palace, townhouse, cape-cod
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, quad-bike, trike, bike
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, video-games, rock-climbing, filmmaking
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goldfish, lizard
4 different games are played: billiard, poker, go, snooker
 1. the person playing snooker is between the person playing go and the palace house##2
 2. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 4. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 8. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 9. the person driving the train is the cape-cod house##1
10. the palace house is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
11. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
14. the palace house is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |       4        |
| House          | cape-cod   | farmhouse        | townhouse      | palace      |
| Transport           | train | trike         | quad-bike   | bike |
| Hobby   | hiking       | rock-climbing          | video-games | filmmaking        |
| Pet           | bird         | chinchilla    | goldfish    | lizard         |
