The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, may, october
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, coral, pink, amber
 1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is in an odd position##4
 3. the dutch is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who likes yellow is the dutch##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the person who likes amber is the mexican##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 9. the indonesian is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating peach is the person who's sport is cricket##1
11. the person who likes amber is in an odd position##4
12. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
13. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
14. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person eating peach and the indonesian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
