 3. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
 4. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
 7. the person who likes coral is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the person who likes lilac is between the fan of metal and the person watching fantasy movies##2
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
11. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
12. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
13. the person who likes blue is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
14. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
