.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-16::.
4 different games are played: canasta, chess, backgammon, billiard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, cricket, swimming, rowing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, electronic, house, indie
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, canadian, german, australian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, disaster, crime, romance
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the egyptian##1
 2. the egyptian is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
 4. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
 5. the person playing canasta is on the left of the german##1
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the canadian is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the person playing billiard is the egyptian##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is between the fan of house and the person who's sport is cricket##2
10. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
11. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
12. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
13. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
14. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Game         | canasta       | chess    | billiard | backgammon     |
| Sport           | rowing | swimming  | cricket  | snowboarding       |
| Music-Genre   | house         | d&b        | indie     | electronic |
| Nationality           | canadian    | german   | egyptian       | australian     |
| Movie-Genre     | romance          | crime | martial-arts      | disaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-17::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, swisher, tiparillo, game
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, bellflower, zinnia, balloon-flower
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, october, april
City: paris, prague, berlin, hannover
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, ship, skateboard
 1. the person traveling to berlin is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is the swisher-smoker##1
 4. the person driving the car is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is between the game-smoker and the person who's birthday is in september##2
 6. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 7. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the person traveling to prague is the person who growszinnia##1
11. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
12. the person traveling to paris is between the person driving the ship and the person traveling to prague##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |     3      |       4       |
| Cigar      | oliveros          | game     | swisher       | tiparillo |
| Flower          | bellflower    | daisy      | zinnia   | balloon-flower          |
| Birthday           | october   | april | august   | september   |
| City   | berlin | paris    | prague     | hannover        |
| Transport     | ship         | quad-bike    | skateboard | car           |

