.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-18::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, soccer, volleyball, skiing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, october, february, april
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, folk, r&b, blues
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, blue, emerald, red
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, taxi, tram
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is the fan of blues##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
 3. the fan of rock is the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person who likes purple is between the person who likes blue and the person who's sport is tennis##2
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the person who likes red is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the fan of folk##1
12. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
13. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
14. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |        4        |
| Sport          | volleyball    | skiing    | soccer     | tennis         |
| Birthday           | november | february | october  | april |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | rock | blues    | r&b          |
| Color           | red  | blue   | purple       | emerald           |
| Transport     | jet-ski | tram      | motorbike | taxi            |

