.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, blood-red, brown, white
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, electronic, techno
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, daisy, iris, amaryllis
City: colone, marseilles, venice, new-york
There 4 different types of food: papaya, blueberry, avocado, pomegranate
 1. the person eating pomegranate is the person who likes grey##1
 2. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 3. the fan of techno is the person eating blueberry##1
 4. the person eating blueberry is the person who likes brown##1
 5. the person traveling to venice is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who likes white is on the far right##1
 7. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person eating avocado##3
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the fan of techno##1
10. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
11. the person traveling to new-york is the person who growsdaisy##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the far left or far right##3
13. the fan of dubstep is between the person who likes white and the person traveling to colone##2
14. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
15. the fan of techno is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |       4       |
| Color      | brown | grey      | blood-red    | white           |
| Music-Genre   | techno   | electronic | dubstep    | ambient       |
| Flower   | amaryllis | iris     | begonia | daisy     |
| City         | venice  | colone    | marseilles | new-york |
| Food     | blueberry     | pomegranate      | avocado     | papaya      |

