.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different games are played: domino, whist, snooker, bridge
City: berlin, colone, prague, liverpool
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, fishing, rock-climbing, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, scientist, librarian, project-manager
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, tiparillo, dunhill, baccarat
 1. the dunhill-smoker is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 3. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 5. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 7. the librarian is the person playing domino##1
 8. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1
 9. the scientist is in an odd position##4
10. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
11. the ritmeester-smoker is between the scientist and the librarian##2
12. the person traveling to liverpool is the person playing bridge##1
13. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who's hobby is baking is the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3     |       4       |
| Game      | domino        | bridge      | snooker | whist         |
| City          | prague      | liverpool      | berlin  | colone         |
| Hobby         | video-games | baking      | fishing  | rock-climbing |
| Job   | librarian      | project-manager | scientist  | bartender        |
| Cigar     | baccarat       | ritmeester        | dunhill  | tiparillo           |

 